  "CitationPopupData" -> $Failed, "ShowCitation" -> False, "HasOptions" -> 
  True, "RootCaptions" -> "", "HeaderCoreAreaLink" -> {}, 
  "Metadata" -> {
   "built" -> "{2026, 4, 12, 17, 57, 40.935556}", 
    "history" -> {"13.3", "", "", ""}, "context" -> "QuantumMob`Q3`", 
    "keywords" -> {"quantum entropy"}, "specialkeywords" -> {}, 
    "tutorialcollectionlinks" -> {}, "index" -> True, "label" -> 
    "Quantum Mob/ Q3 Symbol", "language" -> "en", "paclet" -> "QuantumMob/Q3",
     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "RenyiEntropy[\\[Alpha], {p1, p2, ...}] returns the R\[EAcute]nyi entropy \
of order \\[Alpha] for a random variable associated with probability \
distribution {p1, p2, ...}. RenyiEntropy[\\[Alpha], {p1, p2, ...}, {q1, q2, \
...}] returns the R\[EAcute]nyi divergence (or relative R\[EAcute]nyi \
entropy) of probability distribution {p1, p2, ...} with respect to another \
probability distribution {q1, q2, ...}. RenyiEntropy[\\[Alpha], \\[Rho]] \
returns the quantum R\[EAcute]nyi entropy of order \\[Alpha] for density \
matrix \\[Rho]. RenyiEntropy[\\[Alpha], \\[Rho], \\[Sigma]] returns the \
quantum R\[EAcute]nyi divergence (or relative quantum R\[EAcute]nyi entropy) \
of density matrix \\[Rho] with respect to another density matrix \\[Sigma]. \
RenyiEntropy[\\[Alpha], \\[Rho], {s1, s2, ...}] calculates the quantum R\
\[EAcute]nyi entropy of density operator \\[Rho] acting on system {s1, s2, \
...} of species. RenyiEntropy[\\[Alpha], \\[Rho], {s1, s2, ...}] or \
RenyiEntropy[\\[Alpha], \\[Rho], \\[Sigma], {s1, s2, ...}] calculates the \
quantum R\[EAcute]nyi divergence between density operators \\[Rho] and \
\\[Sigma] acting on system {s1, s2, ...} of species.", "synonyms" -> {}, 
    "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "RenyiEntropy", "titlemodifier" -> "", 
    "metadescription" -> "", "windowtitle" -> "RenyiEntropy", "type" -> 
    "Symbol", "uri" -> "QuantumMob/Q3/ref/RenyiEntropy"}},
